            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "美國股指期貨在清淡交易中微漲 靜候鮑威爾指明政策方向",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"604\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/.qXXDDib_gKcqZUHoxsZ_A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/3c067fedd83d4d8cc8f2e2b529cf2247\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 美股本周以來的連跌勢頭在周五盤前暫歇，<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:聯儲會;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/聯儲會\">聯儲會</a>主席傑羅姆·<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:鮑威爾;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/鮑威爾\">鮑威爾</a>在傑克遜霍爾演講前，市場交易清淡，削減了對聯儲會將很快降息的預期。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">紐約時間6:57，標普500指數和那斯達克100指數期貨上漲0.2%，道指期貨上漲0.3%。此前標普500指數連續五個交易日下跌。歐洲股市上漲0.3%，逼近歷史高點。美國國債周四出現回調後企穩，10年期殖利率報4.33%。美元基本持平。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"鮑威爾周四在傑克遜霍爾。攝影師：David Paul Morris/ 彭博\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/0FznrfrbQE9PZnw49BPmTQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/2b14de105d44635b9c65fd9c5ef4494f\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">鮑威爾周四在傑克遜霍爾。攝影師：David Paul Morris/ 彭博</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">本周科技股的拋售潮使得屢創紀錄的美股上漲走勢暫歇。投資者正等待鮑威爾的最新政策指引，權衡聯儲會是否會繼續對通膨保持謹慎態度 —— 通膨正顯示出頑固的跡象 —— 還是會轉向支持疲軟的勞動力市場。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">掉期市場已顯著降低了聯儲會短期內激進寬鬆的機率，目前市場預計下月降息概率約為65%，今年內降息次數不足兩次。而短短的一周多前，市場還普遍完全消化了9月25個基點的降息，部分交易員甚至押注會降息50個基點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">鮑威爾將於紐約時間上午10點發表講話。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「如果聯儲會9月不降息，市場將下跌，因為市場預期聯儲會會有所行動。如果降息幅度過大，市場可能將其視為聯儲會失去獨立性的信號，這可能引發更高的通膨，」Panmure Liberum策略師Joachim Klement表示。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"604\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/T_ipFzXhYK643eXC4wv59A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/d7784e1907d264db36fbc24e127b02ba\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Stocks Halt Run of Losses Ahead of Powell Address: Markets Wrap</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 James Hirai、Subrat Patnaik.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E8%82%A1%E6%8C%87%E6%9C%9F%E8%B2%A8%E5%9C%A8%E6%B8%85%E6%B7%A1%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E4%B8%AD%E5%BE%AE%E6%BC%B2-%E9%9D%9C%E5%80%99%E9%AE%91%E5%A8%81%E7%88%BE%E6%8C%87%E6%98%8E%E6%94%BF%E7%AD%96%E6%96%B9%E5%90%91-114611910.html",
